reviews.review_msg: Professor Caselli is an amazing. She does her best to make sure everyone succeed in this class. She uses Passapaola platform (costs $100) for online homeworks and quizzes, which makes them very easy to do. Just show up to class and do the homeworks, and you'll be garenteed an A+
Mrs Caselli is one of the greatest profs at SFU, you won't regret taking this class with her.
